* 2x Omloop 't Volk (1971, 1973)
* 2x [[Rounde van Vloandern]] (1969, 1975)
* 3x [[Gent-Wevelgem]] (1967, 1970, 1973)
* 3x [[Parys-Roubaix]] (1968, 1970, 1973)
